text: Sjoerd van Ginneken (born 6 November 1992) is a Dutch former professional racing cyclist, who competed professionally between 2014 and 2019 for the and teams. ==Major results== ;2014 : 3rd Baronie Breda Classic : 4th Overall Czech Cycling Tour ::1st 20px Young rider classification ::1st Stage 1 (TTT) : 8th Overall Okolo Slovenska ::1st 20px Young rider classification ;2018 : 6th Antwerp Port Epic : 7th Druivenkoers Overijse ;2019 : 7th Grote Prijs Jef Scherens : 9th Clásica de Almería : 9th Ronde van Overijssel ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch male cyclists Category:People from Roosendaal Category:Sportspeople from North Brabant
